    "Background": {
      "text": "Inflammation of middle ear spreads into mastoid air cells via the \"aditus ad antrum\"\nVast majority of acute mastoiditis occurs as a result of, or simultaneous with,\nacute otitis media\nMastoiditis is unlikely if middle ear examination is normal",
      "subsections": {
        "Etiology": {
          "text": "S. pneumo\n(22%)\nS. pyogenes\n(16%)\nS. aureus\n(7%)\nH. flu\nP. aeruginosa",
